🌸 CyraSense
A Smart Women’s Health Intelligence Platform
🧠 Overview
CyraSense is a modern web application designed to go beyond basic period tracking. It helps users understand their menstrual health through intelligent pattern analysis, guided insights, and self-care support.
The platform focuses on awareness, early understanding, and safe guidance, rather than diagnosis, making it suitable for everyday users.
🎯 Problem Statement
Many existing apps only track dates but fail to:
Provide meaningful insights
Explain irregular patterns clearly
Support users with actionable guidance
Address pregnancy awareness and cycle delays
Offer a safe, non-alarming experience
As a result, users often feel confused, uninformed, or anxious about their health.
💡 Solution
CyraSense provides:
Smart cycle tracking with predictions
Pattern-based analysis using rule-based logic
Safe, easy-to-understand health insights
Pregnancy awareness and delay detection
Doctor consultation suggestions based on user location
Educational and self-care resources
Gamified learning to improve engagement
⚙️ Key Features
📅 Smart Calendar
Tracks cycle, period days, and ovulation
Predicts future cycles automatically
🧠 Pattern Analysis
Detects cycle irregularities
Analyzes symptoms and trends
Provides non-alarming insights
🤰 Pregnancy Awareness
Detects delays in cycles
Highlights ovulation window
Provides safe informational guidance
🩺 Doctor Suggestions
Recommends consultation when needed
Uses user’s city to suggest doctor type
💬 Chat Assistant
Focused on women’s health topics
Answers questions related to cycles, hygiene, and pregnancy
🧘 Self-Care Section
Exercise and wellness guidance
Hygiene education
Informational content
🎮 Gamified Learning
Quiz-based learning system
Interactive games
Reward points system
🛍 Store
Product browsing
Add-to-cart functionality
Reward-based discounts
⚙️ Settings
Profile management
Theme customization
Privacy controls
🧠 How It Works
CyraSense uses:
Rule-based logic for decision making
Statistical analysis for cycle prediction
User data patterns for personalized insights
The system evaluates:
Cycle length consistency
Symptom repetition
Pain trends
Delays
Based on this, it provides safe suggestions without causing panic.
💾 Data Handling
Data is stored using browser local storage
No external database required
Ensures user privacy and control
Works offline for basic functionality
🎨 UI/UX
Clean and modern design
Soft, feminine color palette
Simple and easy navigation
Designed for everyday usability
🚀 Future Scope
Cloud-based data storage
Real doctor integration
Lab test booking
AI-based report analysis
Mobile app development
⚠️ Disclaimer
CyraSense is not a medical diagnostic tool.
It is designed for awareness and guidance only.
Users are encouraged to consult healthcare professionals for medical concerns.

